get list of folder and files:- dir

jump to inside folder:- cd indra

go back:- cd ..

clear screen :- cls

history of command which we have typed:- get-history

invoke command from history using ID:- invoke-history 4

getting running process:- get-process

getting running process based on name:- get-process notepad

getting running process start from S:- get process s*

start the process:- start-process notepad

stop the process:- stop-process -name notepad

stop processes by id:- stop-process -id 6428

get the process and stop:- get-process notepad | stop-process 

get to know what command is doing:- get-process notepad | stop-process  -whatif


Keys:-

get the command name:- tab
back command:- Shit+tab 
